subject give spiritu gift i just thought i d share a nice experi befor my exam todai i wa walk down the street on our campu and a beggar came up and ask me for ani spare chang i might have i had a dollar or so that i gave her and not want to give awai all my monei to stranger i gener give a dollar as that will bui a littl food at mcdonald or someth i offer her some spiritu gift as i call them rather than gift of monei i talk of how great i felt that god had made such a pretti dai and how nice it wa to give to peopl she then said she wa get marri soon she talk about how she and her husband had veri littl thei mai not have even had a hous for all i know but that thei felt a veri special love in the lord an unselfish kind of care it warm my heart to know that peopl can have so littl monetarili and realiz that spiritu thei ar inde veri rich a good lesson for all of us who sai we want more more more what we realli need cannot be count or sold or bought doug fowler dxf po cwru edu heaven is a great big hug that last forev and when that on great scorer come to mark against your name he write not whether you ve won or lost but how you plai the game grantland rice 